# Tamery architecture

## Monorepo layout

```
apps/api       Hono + oRPC backend (auth, connections, AI, billing, queries)
apps/app       React SPA — main product UI (TanStack Router + TanStack DB)
apps/main      Marketing + auth pages (TanStack Start / Nitro SSR)
apps/desktop   Electron wrapper around apps/app
apps/proxy     oRPC proxy — executes DB queries on behalf of clients
apps/cli       CLI tool published as `tamery` on npm

packages/db            Drizzle schema + migrations (cloud PostgreSQL)
packages/connection    DB driver wrappers, connection-string parsers, SSL/SSH
packages/query-proxy   oRPC router factory shared by apps/api and apps/proxy
packages/ai            Vercel AI SDK tool definitions
packages/ui            Shared React components (shadcn/base-ui)
packages/table         TanStack Virtual table component
packages/shared        Cross-package utils, enums, constants, types
packages/infisical     Secrets client wrapper
packages/configs       Shared ESLint/TypeScript configs
```

## Stack constraints

- **API**: oRPC (`@orpc/server`) — not REST, not tRPC
- **Client state**: TanStack DB collections — not Zustand, not React Context for data
- **Cloud DB**: Drizzle ORM (`packages/db`) — not raw SQL, not Prisma
- **Auth**: Better Auth (`apps/api/lib/auth.ts`) — not custom JWT
- **Secrets**: `@tamery/infisical` — not `.env` in production
- **Runtime**: Bun for all server processes
- **Styles**: TailwindCSS v4 — no inline `style=` for theme values

## Package boundaries

- `packages/connection` — pure driver utils, no Drizzle, no oRPC
- `packages/query-proxy` — oRPC router factory only; imported by both api and proxy apps
- `packages/db` — cloud DB schema only; never imported by desktop/client bundles
- `packages/ai` — AI tool definitions; no DB access
